      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is accompanied with &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/fitness/2025/&#34;&gt;Hope&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is to maintain a daily journal of the efforts. This is to be seen from bottom&#xA;to top.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;To explain the jargons:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;cw: current weight&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;gw: goal weight&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Ok, lets start.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;march-28-2026&#34;&gt;March 28, 2026&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;cw: 83.9&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;I did not do the strength training as planned - but I went out for a walk. These&#xA;days I record the walk both on the Garmin watch &amp;amp; the Strava app.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
